    "overview_number": 7,
    "overview_title": "Playing Ball!",
    "overview_subtitle": "Absolute Value Equations and Inequalities",
    "overview_description": "In this lesson, students estimate the solutions of a linear absolute value function from its graph. They rewrite linear absolute value equations as two linear equations before solving algebraically. Students model a situation with a linear absolute value inequality and its corresponding graph. They rewrite linear absolute value inequalities as equivalent compound inequalities before solving algebraically."
  },
